

- Develop standardized xpaths expressions





- Stop using attrib(...) to get an attribute (relying on different behaviour
  depending on lxml or xml.ElementTree) and use .attrib[] instead



- Change the mzmlMeta.instrument:

	- Format of the instrument serial number:
		either:
	<mzml>
		<instrument(Configuration)List>
			<instrument(Configuration)>
				<referenceableParamGroupRef ref="SOMETHING"/>
			</instrument(Configuration)>
		</instrument(Configuration)List>
		<referenceableParamGroupList>
			<referenceableParamGroup id="SOMETHING">
				<cvParam cvRef="MS" accession="MS:1000529" name="instrument serial number" value="SN06061F"/>													        
				<cvParam cvRef="MS" accession="MS:1000448" name="LTQ FT" value=""/>	 	    ^~~~ serial number
 					instrument name accession ~~~~~~^	 ^~~~ instrument name

			</referenceableParamGroup>
		</referenceableParamGroupList>
	</mzml>

		or:

	<mzml>
		<instrument(Configuration)List>
			<instrument id="LCQ Deca">
				<cvParam cvLabel="MS" accession="MS:1000554" name="LCQ Deca" value=""/>
 					instrument name accession ~~~~~~^	 ^~~~ instrument name                v~~~ serial number
				<cvParam cvLabel="MS" accession="MS:1000529" name="instrument serial number" value="23433"/>
			</instrument>
		</instrument(Configuration)List>
	</mzml>

